I'm just a little paranoid,

39:29.100 --> 39:31.069
especially after coming back
from the hospital, you know.

39:31.102 --> 39:32.070
Yeah.

39:32.103 --> 39:33.371
Plus, Mom would freak.

39:33.405 --> 39:34.940
She's obsessed.
If she had her way,

39:34.973 --> 39:37.409
I would completely
be on bed rest...

39:37.443 --> 39:40.712
which, actually,
does not sound so bad

39:40.746 --> 39:44.049
because, oh, my God,
my feet are killing me.

39:44.082 --> 39:46.251
I keep hearing about some

39:46.284 --> 39:48.554
burst of energy
during the second trimester.

39:48.587 --> 39:49.788
Still waiting.

39:49.821 --> 39:51.557
(groaning)

39:55.661 --> 39:57.963
Oh...

40:02.267 --> 40:03.234
Are you okay?

40:03.268 --> 40:04.736
Oh.
(clears throat)

40:04.770 --> 40:07.072
Yeah, I just feel
like this glass of wine

40:07.105 --> 40:08.907
is getting me light-headed
or something.

40:08.940 --> 40:10.476
Oh, good, good.

40:10.509 --> 40:13.078
Drink up for
the two of us.

40:13.111 --> 40:14.412
(sighs)

40:14.446 --> 40:15.447
(chuckles)

40:16.482 --> 40:18.884
LUCIOUS:
Mom, what are you doing?

40:18.917 --> 40:20.251
It's 3:00 in the morning.

40:22.654 --> 40:24.656
(wind blowing)

40:25.791 --> 40:27.726
What is all of this?

40:27.759 --> 40:29.127
Sit down.

40:42.107 --> 40:43.441
Where's Juanita?

40:43.475 --> 40:45.310
I sent her away.

40:45.343 --> 40:47.445
You know I don't
like anyone else

40:47.479 --> 40:48.780
cooking in my kitchen.

40:48.814 --> 40:50.448
You can't send her away.

40:50.482 --> 40:51.449
She lives here.

40:51.483 --> 40:52.484
She works for me.

40:52.518 --> 40:53.985
Not anymore.

40:56.522 --> 41:00.158
Sit down.

41:09.735 --> 41:11.870
Eat it.

41:11.903 --> 41:13.304
I'm not hungry.

41:13.338 --> 41:16.508
I won't ask again.

41:20.712 --> 41:21.980
I slaved

41:22.013 --> 41:23.348
for hours in that kitchen,

41:23.381 --> 41:25.817
baking these cakes for you.

41:27.052 --> 41:29.988
And what do you
do to repay me?

41:31.222 --> 41:34.526
You leave me all by myself.

41:34.560 --> 41:35.694
All alone.

41:35.727 --> 41:37.228
All day.

41:37.262 --> 41:38.496
Look, I have to work.

41:38.530 --> 41:40.065
Everybody leaves.

41:40.098 --> 41:41.833
First your father...

41:41.867 --> 41:43.168
No, my father didn't leave.

41:43.201 --> 41:44.870
He was murdered.
I saw it.

41:44.903 --> 41:47.372
Who brought all this
wickedness into our lives?

41:48.406 --> 41:49.841
You.

41:51.076 --> 41:54.680
I was fine until
you were born.

41:54.713 --> 42:00.351
All my troubles
came with you.

42:01.553 --> 42:03.589
Who told you to stop eating?

42:14.733 --> 42:17.235
Well?

42:17.268 --> 42:19.738
It's good.

42:22.908 --> 42:25.243
Do you love me?

42:33.418 --> 42:34.920
Liar.

42:34.953 --> 42:36.888
If you loved me,
you wouldn't have

42:36.922 --> 42:40.425
put me away
for 21 years.

42:40.458 --> 42:41.893
You were sick.

42:41.927 --> 42:44.730
You said so yourself.

42:44.763 --> 42:47.398
I was sick.

42:47.432 --> 42:51.569
Now I'm sorry.

42:51.603 --> 42:54.439
Sorry I was too weak

42:54.472 --> 42:57.075
to kill you
when I had the chance.

43:54.833 --> 43:55.801
Yeah.

